hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Incorrect PIN hull pharmacy bank holiday weekend 2017 “If a company is getting a lot of publicity just because they have market share or what have you, whatever they announce is going to get more attention. I don’t know that manifests itself as a reflection of how good or how bad the product is going to be. It’s just more visibilitiy. Do I like the situation? Not really, but if you take the PlayStation business every announcement we make gets huge amounts of publicitity because we’re in that leadership positions. In some businesses we get a lot more attention, that’s the reality.”
